{
  "stem": "17001.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 152.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And meantime, my aunt, my mother younger sister, who lived in Kisvarda, she had heard what goes on and so on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she knew that we were taken in, so she had workers-- because they were very well-to-do people, they had workers.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she had sent cook food and he gave it over the fence, so we had cook food.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then later on, when they were taken into the ghetto from their home, then she send message that we should go to the house where they are, because instead of to have strange people laying next to her-- because what they did, they closed off a certain area where it was mostly Jewish population, but there were also non-Jews who lived there.",
      "word_count": 63
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they had relocated the non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the meantime, the way they were gathering the people from all over the area, they were putting it into these houses.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So my aunt was in one of the house like this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we went over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We left our quarters in the shul and we went over to my aunt.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we made the room on the-- on the floor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there was about four other families in the same room.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But before you went into our room, you had to go through two, three other rooms, because this house belonged to a very rich family, so there were people that-- if you wanted to go to the bathroom, that you had to go through the bodies and you had to watch you shouldn't step over them.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, there was this family who were two boys and a girl and the mother.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
